.claude/
*.tmp.*

# stray tool output (accidental agent/CLI runs in repo root)
/assets/
*$LOG*

# coderecall transient runtime state (per-machine, never committed)
.ai/memory/.heartbeat
.ai/memory/.reminder
.ai/memory/.lock/


# >>> coderecall (per-developer working state — local, not committed) >>>
# Committed by default: DECISIONS.md, LESSONS.md, archive/consolidated-*, archive/retired-*
# (durable, team-valuable). The lines below are volatile/per-developer — keep them local.
# Want a solo private repo to track live task state too? Delete the TASK.md/sessions.md lines.
.ai/memory/TASK.md
.ai/memory/sessions.md
.ai/memory/archive/precompact-*.md
.ai/memory/.heartbeat
.ai/memory/.reminder
.ai/memory/.lock/
# <<< coderecall <<<
